Phoenix Project
Wordcount Example Application Readme
Last revised May 15, 2011


1. Application Overview
-----------------------

The WordLength application counts the frequency of occurence of sizes of words
in a text document, from 'small' to 'medium' and 'large'.


2. Provided Files
-----------------

word_length.cpp: The application
Makefile: Compiles the application
datafiles/*.txt: Sample text files of varying sizes that can be used as 
                 input to this application (download from the website)
README: This file


3. Running the Application
--------------------------

Run 'make' to compile the application. 

./word_length <text_file>

runs the application.


End File
